{"tid":1063922,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李東海小學校長疑不堪壓力 入住沙田醫院精神科病房","createTime":"2019-03-16T06:50:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-16T08:18:01.000Z","uid":129474,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"86994faa7dd32157bb16d1f33a023a9949840d14","tid":1063922,"uid":129474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T06:50:46.000Z","msg":"天水圍東華三院李東海小學女教師疑不堪壓力，上周三（6日）在校內墮樓身亡，後來被校內其他教師揭發死者生前屢遭校長羅婉儀壓迫，事發前一日更被召到校長室責罵，被勒令要重寫「悔過書」。事件曝光後，輿論矛頭指向羅婉儀校長，羅一直沒有公開回應事件，並於周日（10日）起向校方請假。消息指，備受批評的羅婉儀，懷疑不堪壓力，日前到威爾斯親王醫院急症室求診，再被轉介到沙田醫院精神科，目前入住該院精神科病房。<br />\n<br />\n記者今早到過沙田醫院精神科病房擬探望羅校長，病房護士先查問記者是否在病人的探病名單內，該名單只列有羅婉儀的親人名字，其後另一名護士聽到記者是前來探羅婉儀後，即改口稱病房內並無此病人，並着記者離開。病房內有一名方型臉戴眼鏡的中年女病人，戴着口罩半臥在病床上看雜誌，但記者未能確認她是否羅婉儀。<br />\n<br />\n女教師墮樓事件曝光後，羅婉儀一直未有露面回應及解釋，並隨即休假，東華三院成立獨立調查委員會處理事件，隨後羅的facebook個人帳戶工作狀態亦改為李東海小學的「前任女校長」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190316&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59375361\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190316%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59375361&d=hEl8YzVD%2FOsYsQiwoICJnPkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=0ac8bff3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190316%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59375361&h=a7c0d8f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190316&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59375361</a>"},{"pid":"050162258a3421f8e92f9d6757bd8ec1aa367f7c","tid":1063922,"uid":164167,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T06:51:09.000Z","msg":"抵啦"},{"pid":"0bf2e02cefeb00a2b1e7351889da31662b45e445","tid":1063922,"uid":25538,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T06:51:31.000Z","msg":"扮病"},{"pid":"aceda8a2db54056d7df3d862ceb7d7f8dc7782fd","tid":1063922,"uid":41035,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T06:51:32.000Z","msg":"扮晒野？"},{"pid":"2660e101624e3331295c3ed6c0206c18045aa2ac","tid":1063922,"uid":104502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T06:52:04.000Z","msg":"俾鬼搞"},{"pid":"891e3ee39d2b16089b375126a9a2b6309ed69083","tid":1063922,"uid":77606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T06:52:08.000Z","msg":"校長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果痴痴的等某日終於可等到一生中最愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ded82540180d0e76ec2ab12f5cae78e48086f1ff","tid":1063922,"uid":120123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T06:52:36.000Z","msg":"插水?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n唔好扮慘，比你逼死果個老師命都冇埋。想扮下精神病就算?"},{"pid":"ac309130b1d22bb1ad230f1d5d3c701b51ca029e","tid":1063922,"uid":196735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T06:53:56.000Z","msg":"唔好比佢停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 剃人頭者，人亦剃其頭"},{"pid":"4dc9db963c59871d9d430e8069ce048c81abf8f6","tid":1063922,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T06:54:14.000Z","msg":"扮傻？"},{"pid":"0a96d3295252ca9ac357479f0aa914353ad1e64c","tid":1063922,"uid":87339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T06:54:31.000Z","msg":"病房內有一名方型臉戴眼鏡的中年女病人，戴着口罩半臥在病床上看雜誌，但記者未能確認她是否羅婉儀。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dec6e1ce9b55b46a2332f7797466c5c3a765848e","tid":1063922,"uid":45428,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T06:55:11.000Z","msg":"諗左兩個禮拜先諗到扮傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"581db8da5c8fbd7107392eed12d20b8146da0156","tid":1063922,"uid":130456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201